                               QUICK TIPS A - Z

Typed by SIDEWINDER of LSD.


AFTERBURNER
Pause the game and type 'THUNDERBLADE'.  Unpause and use the following keys
for various effects:
'G' - extra missiles, '<' - jump forward a stage, '>' - jump back a stage, and
'N' extra lives.

AFTER THE WAR
During the first stage, press ALT+B+1 for infinite energy and time or ALT+M+1
to jump to the second stage.

AMC
A few access codes:
NOSTROMO, DISCOVERY, ENTERPRISE, DAGOBAH, REPLICANT, KRULL, METROPOLIS.

APB
Type 'ALF' into the hi-score table for infinite demerits.

ARCHIPELAGOS
When asked to select an Archipelago, choose 8421 and then press ENTER twice.
Now you can select any island from 1 to 9999.

ARKANOID
For an extra thirty-three levels, type F3 for a one player game and F4 for a
two player game (instead of F1 and F2)

ARKANOID II
Press Capslock then type 'DALEY88' for infinite lives.  Alternatively, on the
title screen, type 'PETEJOHNSONWANTSCHEAT' (no spaces) and 'S' will open the
exits at any point.

ARMY MOVES
The code for part two is 101069.  In the first part hold down ALT+1+D for
immunity, and for the same effect in the second part, hold down ALT+1+J.

ATOMIC ROBOKID
On the title screen type 'TUESDAY 14th' for a cheat menu.

ATOMIX
Hit HELP to enter password mode and enter 'TIME' for a frozen stop watch.

AWESOME
At the energy swap screen, move the pointer over to where you get your shield.
Now hold down '+' on numeric keypad and press fire.  The screen should flash
and now during play F1-F10 will give you all the different weapons, F1 will
disable enemies, and F6 will restore energy.

BAAL
Type in 'LOVEBUNDLE' as your name in the hi-score chart to use the game's
in-built trainer mode.

BACK TO THE FUTURE II
Pause the game and type 'THE ONLY NEAT THING TO DO' (with spaces) and you
should have infinite lives while Z will skip a level.

BARBARIAN (Psygnosis)
Press '0', then '4', then the left hand minus sign.  Then press '0', and '8',
and the minus sign again.  Now press '5' and '9' to become invincible.

BATMAN THE MOVIE
Type 'JAMMMM' on the title screen for infinite lives, and pressing F10 will
skip levels.

BATTLE SQUADRON
Type in 'CASTOR' while playing and the border will flash.  Now you'll be
immune to energy loss while F6-F10 will cycle through the weapons and F1-F5
will cycle through the power settings.

BATTLE VALLEY
Type 'ROGER MELLIE THE MAN ON THE TELE' (with spaces) for infinite tanks.

BEACHVOLLEY
Type 'DADDYBRACEY' while playing so that F1 will advance you to the next
level.

BETTER DEAD THAN ALIEN
During the game if the odds are against you and everything's pointing to you
being obliterated within the next three picoseconds, press ESC to pause and
move your ship to a safe area.  'N' will continue.

BEVERELY HILLS COP
Click past the hi-score screen onto the select difficulty page.  Type 'MELLIE'
and you will be able to access all the games.

BIO-CHALLENGE
Pause with ESC and then 'G' will advance you to the end of level guardian
(that's just in case you want to go there).

BOMBUZAL
Some level codes:
ROSS, TREE, RATT, LISA, SINK, DAVE, BIKE, IRON, BIRD, LEAD, TAPE, WEED, VASE,
RING, PILL, GIRL, SPOT, GOLD, PALM, OPAL, LOCK, SONG, SAFE, FIRE, WORM, LAMP.

BSS JANE SEYMOUR
Level Codes:
SLUMBER, INTEREST, BULKHEAD, SHOWROOM, MUSHBASH.

CARRIER COMMAND
During the game, pause and type 'GROW OLD ALONG WITH ME' (plus spaces).  Then
'+' and '-' will toggle immunity.  If you find that one a tad boring, then try
typing 'THE BEST IS YET TO BE' and use the same keys to view all the objects.

CABAL
Type SCHLIKA during play.  The border will flash and now F2 finishes the
level.

CHARIOTS OF WRATH
When instructed to press FIRE to start, rebelliously move the joystick forward
instead.  Result: Infinite lives.

CHASE HQ
At any point, hold down the left mouse button and joystick fire button, while
typing 'GROWLER'.  Afterwards 'T' during the game will reset your time to 60
seconds.

CHUBBY GRISTLE
On the title screen, type 'BUUURRP' for infinite lives.

CONTINENTAL CIRCUS
When the first red light comes on at the starting line push the joystick
forward, then back for the next red light, then forward again on green for a
good start.

CRACKDOWN
During play, pause the game and enter 'SMURF'.  Pressing F1 and F2 will now
reimburse both player's lives.

CYBERNOID
Type 'RAISTLIN' on the title screen for infinite lives.

CYBERNOID II
Type 'NECRONOMIOCON' on the title screen for infinite lives.

DEFENDER OF THE CROWN
Holding down 'K' while booting the second disk gives you realms and realms of
extra knights.

DEFENDER II
Type 'GOATY' to make yourself invincible.  Try these level codes:
LEMAC, ZIPPO, LAZER, DAFAD, MAMOG, FUNKY and DONKY.

DENARIS
When the data disk prompt is displayed, insert data disk and hold down 'Z'
while it loads, then put the mouse into the joystick port and start the game
and remember to hold down the mouse button while it loads.

DOGS OF WAR
Type 'TIMBO' before you start and F5 will provide you with infinite lives.

DOMINATOR
Type your name as 'SHAFT' on the hi-score table for infinite lives.

DRAGON BREED
At the end of a level, while the next one is loading, hold down the left mouse
button, DELETE and HELP together.  When the screen flashes you can skip levels
by whacking one of the keys on your keyboard.

DRAGON NINJA
During the game type 'TERRIFIC'.  Now, 'F3' gives infinite lives and 'L' the
next level.

DRAGONSCAPE
While playing, hold down ALT+DOWN, the cursor will advance you a level.

DRAGON'S LAIR
On the credit screen, press Return and then type 'GET MORDROC DIRK' (with
spaces).
Alternatively, after the credit sequence hold down ESC,R,/,L,N and 7
simultaneously to allow the computer to finish the game for you.

DRAKKHEN
Load the character disk, select a gender, for the name type '3145927'.  Press
ENTER then type in 'SUPERVISOR' then enter again.  Now during play, F9 pauses
and replenishes hit points while F9 shows you something (oo-er).

DRILLER
When you start the game you will be facing a small shed-like building.  Shoot
it 20+ times and you'll be transformed into a jet and consequently, you'll be
able to fly around the Freescape world.

DRIVIN' FORCE
On the menu click on the two 'I's of 'DRIVIN'.
Start the game and your vehicle will be stuck to the track like glue.

DYNAMITE DUX
Type 'CHEAT' on the title screen to recieve infinate lives.  Press F1 to F6 to
skip levels and type 'NUDE' to play the boxing sub-game.

DYNASTY WARS
On the title screen type 'CHEAT MODE'.  Now when playing press F2 to skip a
level.

DYTER-07
While the game is loading type in 'GIBB'.  Now, during play, press 'W' to
receive extra weapons or 'S' to top up your shield.

ELIMINATOR
Some level codes:
AMOEBA, BLOOOP, CHEEKI, DOINOK, ENIGMA, FLIPME, GEEGEE, HANDEL, ICICLE,
HAMMIN, KIKONG, LAPDOG (this one gives you infinite lives) and MIKADO.

ELITE
When asked for the first code-word from the manual type 'SARA' followed by
ENTER.  Type the correct word at the next prompt.  Now, at any time during the
game, pressing the * key will put you into the cheat bank.  You will be asked
for a two digit byte, and then a two digit value.  Use the following:
18-FF (quite a large amount of cash), 24-01 (ECM system), 2F-01 (Energy Bomb),
32-01 (Docking Computer), 38-01 (Military laser), and 3F-01 (Cloaking Device).
ESC puts you back into the game.

E-MOTION
Type in the name of the game on the title screen.  Now F1 advances a level, F2
moves on 10 levels, F3 goes back a level, and F4 goes back 10 levels.

EMPIRE STRIKES BACK
On the title screen hold down 'HELP' and type 'XIFARGROTCEV'.  Various keys
now do various things during the game, especially 'L', 'C', and 'D' which
conjure up pictures of Luke, C3P0 and Darth Vader respectively.

ENCHANTED LAND
Type 'TCB RULES FOREVER' on the intro screen and the screen will flash.
Pressing F3 will allow you to enter an edit.  Pressing F2 followed by a space
will take you to the end of level guardian.

E-SWAT
Pause during the game and type in 'JUSTIFIED ANCIENTS OF MU MU' (try it with
or without spaces).  The border will flash and you'll be endowed with 99
lives.

EYE OF HORUS
Type 'SPAM' on the credit section for infinite lives and no need for keys.

EXOLON
Type your name as 'AD ASTRA' on the hi-score table for a surprise cheat.

FALCON
In flight, hold down 'X', 'SHIFT' and 'CONTROL' to be fully rearmed.

FERNANDEZ MUST DIE
During the game, pause and type 'SPINYNORMAN' (no spaces) for infinite
assasination attempts.

F-19 STEALTH FIGHTER
Press ALT-H to get the pitch lines on your HUD, fly upside down, turn off your
engines, keep your plane about 10 degrees on your HUD and watch that baby
climb.

F-29 RETALIATOR
1.      Type in 'THE DIDY MEN' as your name on the duty roster.  Now 'ENTER' will
        land your plane for you.
2.      When you get killed on a mission, instead of restarting the game, wait
        until the 'Service Terminated' screen appears and reset your computer.
        Reload the game and your pilot should be intact.
3.      Set up your mission as normal but do not enter the weapons selection
        screen.  Now when you start your mission you will have unlimited
        Thunderbolt missiles.  Fire away!

FIGHTER BOMBER
Type in your pilot's name as 'BUCKAROO'.  You can now advance to any mission
you like.  Hit 'D' at any time during your flight to be whisked to your next
target.

FLYING SHARK
Gain a high score and then type:
RLH (for acid men), JGL (full fire power, KDJ (infinite lives) and RAB (for
immunity)
NOTE: You must hold down '5' on the numeric keypad while you type the last
letter.

FLOOD
Level codes:
FROG, YEAR, QUIF, LONG, WORD, FRED, WINE, GRIP, TRAP, THUD, FRAK, VINE, JUMP,
NILL, FOUR, GRIT, JING, ZING, LIDO, POOL, HATE, REED, LIME, QUID, and WING.
If you can't be bothered with all that malarkey, type in the password 'SOAP'
and select any level to play on.

FORGOTTEN WORLDS
Type 'ARC' on the title screen then press the HELP key.  Now while playing,
'S' takes you instantly to the shop while 'N' teleports you to the next level.

GAME OVER
The access code for level two is 11423.

GAUNTLET
To select any level, choose your player and press start.  When you appear on
level one, don't budge a millimetre.  Instead press Option 1.

GAUNTLET II
While adventuring, find a treasure chest and make sure you have a key.  Hold
down INSERT when you open the chest.  Release INSERT, and hold the joystick
down.  Now the HELP key will give you 5000 health points.

GHOSTBUSTERS II
When the word 'Activision' appears on the screen press CTRL+ALT+S+U for a
variety of effects.

GHOSTS 'N' GOBLINS
When the credit screen appears, type 'DELBOY'.  The words 'CHEAT MODE
ACTIVATED' will appear on the screen and you will be invincible.

GHOULS AND GHOSTS
Type 'KAREN BROADHURST' for infinite lives.

GRAVITY FORCE
When asked for the password, type WARP?? instead (where ?? is the number of
the wanted level)

GREMLINS 2
Type 'SINATRA' on the high score chart.

HAMMERFIST
Get a hi-score and type in 'TAEHC OT TNAW I' (with spaces).  Now F7 will
teleport you to the next level of play.

HARD DRIVIN'
Make sure you're in manual mode for gears, then accelerate to full speed.
When you're at top speed, change to neutral gear.  You should now be
invincible to collisions.

HAWKEYE
When you are on the brink of death with no lives, press DELETE to be magically
transported to the next level.  Also, during the game, press pause, push HELP,
then unpause and you should have infinite lives.

HELTER SKELTER
Level codes:
SPIN, FLIP, GOAL, LEFT, TWIN, PLAY.
In the two player mode, if one player gets EXTRA, simply ley the time run down
until one player loses all their lives.  That way, it's infinite lives all
round.

HORROR ZOMBIES FROM THE CRYPT
Hold down 'M' and ',' and '.' for infinite lives.

HYBRIS
If you type 'COMMANDER' on the hi-score table, F10 will toggle immunity, F9
will teleport you to the next level and F2-F8 equips you with the add-ons.

IKARI WARRIORS
Type 'FREERIDE' for invincibility.

IMMORTAL
Level codes:
cddff10006f70 (level two)
