IMPOSSAMOLE
Type the following words on the hi-score table for a myriad of effects:
HEINZ (three power bars), OUCH OUCH (walk on water), COMMANDO (infinite weapon
time), ANNFRANK (energy top up), LUMBAJACK (double size energy bar) and
JUGGLERS.

INDIANA JONES
Type 'SILLYNAM' as your name on the hi-score table for continuous continue
option.  Also, type 'IEHOVA' when the title screen comes up.  The border will
flash grey to tell you the cheat is activated.  Then '2' will advance you
through the flash-points of the level, 'L' will move you to the next scene and
'I' supplies you with an icon.

INTERPHASE
During the game type 'Fenny' (with Capshift on the F').  Then the left mouse
button will cycle through the objects, the right button will enlarge the
object and both will take you back to the game.

IVANHOE
Pause the game and type in 'ZOMBINETTE' and press Return.  Now pressing 'N'
will advance you a level.

JAMES POND
Type in JUNKYARD and press Return.  Now you can toggle the cheat mode on/off
by pressing Return, and you can make the inter level locks disappear by
pressing 'D'.

KARATE KID II
Pressing 'P' skips levels.

KICK OFF 2
Keep pressing 'R' when you take a penalty.  This will show you where the
player's going to kick the ball.

KID GLOVES
Pause the game and type in 'RHIANNON' then F6 will take you back to the shop,
F8 will give you loads of money, and F9 toggles immunity.

KLAX
Hold down Shift and Space together and press 1-4 for fun and games which
include inexhaustable credits and the means to go straight to level 100.  To
play the last screen hold down CTRL+4 during the game.

LAST DUEL
Start the game, pause with F9 and then hold down HELP and LEFT-SHIFT and 1,
unpause - the function keys will now take you through the levels and F8 gives
you five lives.

LEATHERNECK
During the game, type 'CUTHBERTNECK' and then F3 to be immune from all
attacks.

LED STORM
Type 'DAVID BROADHURST  WANTS TO CHEAT' for infinite lives.

LEMMINGS
On the title screen type 'FQUIGGLY' to activate the cheat modes, or
alternatively, try the following fun codes:
IJJLDNCCN, NJLDCADCY, JNLHCIOECY, DLBIKNLGCT, HBANLLDHCJ, BIONNLHICP,
BEJHMDHJCY, MJJOLLBKCR, NMHDHBALCK, HMDHBINMCT, MDHBAJNLCM, DHBIJLMOCV,
