LIGHT CORRIDOR
Level codes:
0000, 5400, 0101, 3901, 2602, 9902, 4303, 9003, 6904, 3305.

LOTUS ESPRIT TURBO CHALLENGE
Enter player one's name as 'FIELDS OF FIRE' (with spaces) and player two's as
'IN A BIG COUNTRY' to carry on playing even if you come last, or for a fab
'novelty' effect, enter player one as 'MONSTER' and player two as 'SEVENTEEN'.
This will take you to a completely different game - a vertical scrolling
shoot-em up.

MANIC MINER 2
Pause the game with the Space Bar, press the asterisk key and then unpause,
you now have nine extra lives.

MENACE
Type 'XR3iTURBONUTTERBASTARD' at some point during the game.

