NINJA SPIRIT
For complete invulnerability press F9 to pause.  Then hit CAPSLOCK and hold
down CTRL and SHIFT.  The game should now reset and you will be blessed with
invulnerability.

NINJA WARRIORS
During the game, press CAPSLOCK, type the code, then CAPSLOCK again.  The
codes to try to follow are;
MONTY PYTHON, SKIPPY, A SMALL STEP FOR MAN, THE TERMINATOR, and STEVE AUSTIN.

NITRO
Type in your name as 'MAJ' to get 5,000 fuel and 50 credits.

OLYMPIC CHALLENGE
Type 'HINGSEN.J' and then the function keys will select any event.

OOOPS UP
