OPERATION THUNDERBOLT
Hit the following keys in sequence to have the laser sight throughout the
game:
F8,F7,F6,F5,F4,F3,F8,F1,F1,F1 (one player game)
F8,F7,F6,F5,F4,F3,F8,F2,F2,F2 (two player game)
Alternatively, type 'WIGAN NINJA' as your name in the hi-score chart for
infinite lives, F2 next level, alternatively (again!!), type SPECCY MODE to
play in Speccy mode.

OUTRUN
While playing type 'RED BARCHETTA' then T for additional time or G to advance
a stage.

PACLAND
On the title screen type 'AVALON' for infinite pacmen.

PLATOON
On the title screen type in 'HAMBURGER HILL'.  Then, during the game, F2 to go
straight to the explosive, F3 to go 'as the crow flies' to the bridge, F4 to
find the village and F5 to gain immunity from everything.

RAINBOW ISLANDS
Type in the following codes on the title screen for the following effects:
BLRBJSBJ - fast feet, RJSBJSBR - double rainbow, SSSLLLRS - fast rainbows,
BJBJBJRS - first hint, LJKSKBLS - continue all rounds, SJBLRJSR - slow meanies
down.
For infinite lives, choose three credits, hold down 'QWERTY' keys and press
your joystick button.  When the game loads you should have infinite lives.

RAMBO III
Type in 'RENEGADE' on the high score table then press 1, 2, or 3 for the
levels.

RETURN OF THE JEDI
Type 'DARTH VADER' as your name on the hi-score table then press F2 to skip
levels.

RICK DANGEROUS
On the hi-score table type 'POOKY'.  Find out what happens for yourself.

ROADBLASTERS
While playing type 'LAVILLASTRANGIATO' then 1-4 will select the different
weapons, S for the next stage and F for fuel.

ROBOCOP
Pause and type 'BEST KEPT SECRET' (with spaces) for immunity.

ROBOCOP 2
When the intro music begins to play, type 'SERIALINTERFACE'.  A screen should
appear telling you about the cheat.  Try this one as well:
Once loaded, press F3 to access the hi-score table and then type in
'BAMBOOZULEM' followed by Help.  You should have infinite energy.  When you're
in the shooting gallery don't move the joystick and you will have shot 1186
targets.

R-TYPE
Type your name as 'SUMITA.' (don't forget the full stop at the end) for
infinite lives.

SATAN
Hold down ALT+1+D during game one and you receive infinite lives.  Do the same
to ALT+1+M during game two for infinite lives and credits.

SCORPION
Get a high score, type 'IMPORTLIGAT' for ten lives.

SDI
Type 'ALERIC' on the hi-score table then function keys select level.

SHADOW WARRIORS
While the intro sequence is running use all three hands and hold down the
following; (CTRL,J,ESC,5,F2,RIGHT ALT,V,ENTER (not Return) and HELP.  Your
purple flashing border will tell you that you are now in cheat mode.  1 and 2
give both players extra energy, Help skips levels and Q makes you invincible.

SHINOBI
Pause the game then type 'LARSXViii' for infinite credits.

SILKWORM
Either hold down HELP and press fire to start the game, or if that doesn't
work, type 'SCRAP 28' on the control options screen for infinite lives.

SIM CITY
Put Capslock on and type 'FUND' to gain $10,000
NOTE: Do this more than three times will cause an earthquake.

SOLOMON'S KEY
Type 'HELP' when it says 'PRESS ANY KEY TO LOAD'.

SORCERY+
Type 'GAS MASK WHEELER WANTS CHEAT' with spaces at some point during the game.

SLYSPY
Enter the code number as 0-0-7 and then during the game type 'SHAKEN NOT
STIRRED' for infinate credits.

THE SPY WHO LOVED ME
Type 'MISS MONEYPENNY' on the title screen for infinite lives.

STARGLIDER II
Pause in mid-game and type 'WE'RE ON A MISSION FROM GOD'.  Try without
apostrophe if it doesn't work.

STARRAY
On the options screen type 'AL YANKOVIC'.  Press F5 for effect.  Also X, C, T
and SPACE produces a cheat screen.

ST DRAGON
Hold down left mouse button and fire button until the game loads for infinite
lives.  Alternatively, during play, press Capslock and type 'DECAFFINATED' and
then Return for the very same infinite lives.

STREET FIGHTER
Type in 'STREET CHEAT' during the game and see what happens.

STRIDER
Start the game then pause with F9.  Hold down HELP and LEFT-SHIFT and 1
together.  Unpause and now 1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 will take you to the respective
level while F1, F2, F3 and F4 will advance you through the current level.

STYRX
At some point hold down HELP and M and E for infinite energy, all the previous
keys and P for all the passes and all the previous keys plus F10 to see the
end of the game.

SUPER CARS
When asked to type in your name try these variations: RICH (for half a million
credits), ODIE (for level 2) and BIGC (for level 3)

SUPER HANG-ON
Type 750J on the hi-score table.  Then press CTRL and ALT and Z and T to reach
the next screen.

SUPREMACY
If you scrap a solar satellite on a planet with no reserves of fuel, you will
gain 30,000 tons of the stuff.

SWITCHBLADE
Type 'POOKY' into the hi-score table and then hold down 1, 2, 3, 4 or 5, click
on 'End' to exit the score table and continue clicking through the opening
screens, still holding down the key.  This will allow five different entry
points to the game.

SWORD OF SODAN
Type 'NANCY' into the hi-score table for infinite lives and press ENTER to
skip levels.

TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES
When asked for a code, type 8859, and then type 1506, and the third time give
the correct code.  During play press Help for infinite lives.

THE GATES OF JAMBALA
Not the simplest of cheat modes, this.  On the title screen type (with spaces)
'YICKE YACKE H[HNERKACKE' hold down the left shift button, hold down '1',
release '1', release left shift.  The title should turn to blue.  Go to the
game.  Keys 1-7 take you to the levels, F1-F5 select weapons and G to give you
gold.  Check out the other function buttons too...

THUNDERBLADE
Type 'CRASH' on the title screen then HELP advances you a level.

TIME MACHINE
Type 'DIZZY' into the hi-score charts for infinite lives.

TOTAL ECLIPSE
Hold down 1 and 9 and press FIRE to see the firework display.

TORVAK THE WARRIOR
Type 'CHEAT....' (as many fullstops as you can fit in) into the hi-score
chart.  Then hold down fire and press 1-5 to be magically teleported between
levels.

TOYOTA CELICA GT RALLY
When you start a race hold down Control and 'C' to stop your time.  Also, when
you crash, immediately press Help.  This will take you to the options screen
which you should exit instantly with fire.  You can now restart your engine
without the 20 second penalty.

TRAILBLAZER
Hold down HELP and I and 1 and 2 then type 'CHEAT'.
Now: F3 - removes gravity, F5 - changes ball shapes, F6 - changes other
player's ball, and HELP to hear laugh.

UNTOUCHABLES
On the title screen type SOUTHAMPTONGAZETTE (no spaces) and it should flash at
the bottom of the screen.  Press F10 and you'll go to the next level.  In
levels 2, 3 and 6 with cheat mode activated, press HELP and it'll take you to
halfway through the level you're on.

VENUS THE FLYTRAP
Press the Spacebar on the title page and type in the following planets:
MERCURY (continouos flight), PLUTO (infinite ammo), JUPITER (infinite time),
MARS (all weapons).
For access to levels try:
MANTIDS, CICADAS, PSYLLIDS, PIERIDS, SATYRIDS, LYCAENID, PYRALID, and NOCTUID.

VIGILANTE
Type your name as 'GREEN CRYSTAL' in the hi-score table so that F1 will
increase lives and F8 will whisk you away to the next level.

VIRUS
Hold down ENTER on the keypad and press P to pause.  Keep ENTER pressed and
press O to unpause.  Now C to toggle special FX on/off, L to add one missile,
F to replenish the fuel, D for demo on/off and finally N for cheat on/off.

VOYAGER
On the options screen type 'WHEN THE SWEET SHOWERS OF APRIL FALL' to activate
the cheat.

WEIRD DREAMS
During the game, in the hallway, when you're halfway through a mirror, tap out
a morse code of 'SOS' on the HELP key.

WINGS OF FURY
Select your rank as usual, then, when on the carrier, type 'COLIN WAS HERE'
(with spaces).  Then C changes weapons in flight, M gives you infinite
weapons, press P for an extra life, D makes you immune and F fully fuels you.

WIZBALL
Type 'RAINBOW' during the game.  Then pause and press C to fill the pot, S to
complete the level, and T to complete the game.

X-OUT
Buy the most expensive ship and place it on the grid.  Now select the cheapest
satellite and place it on the money indicator.  You should have half a million
credits.  Press Escape key at any point to take you up to the next level.

XYBOTS
Type 'ALF' on the hi-score table to get infinite energy.

Z-OUT
Press J and K simultaneously for infinite energy.  Then press J and any number
between 1 and 6 to skip levels, or 1 and 3 on the numeric keypad to jump
sections.

End.
